				<title>Version 2.1.5</title>
				<description><![CDATA[
					<h2>Bugfixes and a new feature</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Fixed encoding problem with attribution handling</li>
						<li>Fixed problem with attribution using integer-based values (like <i>.year</i>, <i>.month</i>, ...)</li>
						<li>Fixed problem with linebreaks not being shown in attributions</li>
						<li>The custom attribution textfields in the preferences now allow entering linebreaks without having to hold <i>Option</i></li>
					</ul>
