			<item>
				<title>Version 2.1.1</title>
				<description><![CDATA[
					<h2>New attribution variables + bugfix</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>
							Added new attribution variables:
							<ul>
								<li><b>${message.from}</b>: same as <em>${message.sender}</em></li>
								<li><b>${message.from.name}</b>: name of sender (as set in From-header)</li>
								<li><b>${message.from.email}</b>: e-mail address of sender</li>
								<li><b>${response.from}</b></li>
								<li><b>${response.from.name}</b></li>
								<li><b>${response.from.email}</b></li>
							</ul>
						</li>
						<li>Fixed bug in encoding of certain attribution parameters, which
							caused <em>${message.sender}</em> not to show the e-mail address
							but only the name of the sender (if any)</li>
					</ul>
				]]></description>
				<pubDate>Thu Jun  2 13:58:10 2011 CEST</pubDate>
